race.description: Road To Magic Millions Book Now Mdn Hcp
race.comment: TULONG (1) is unlucky to still be a maiden placing in all three runs this preparation and strikes a very winnable contest here. Has placed over this track and trip and should be right there when the whips are cracking. BON VADER (2) has been thereabouts in both starts to date and gets gun hoop Maloney on board from the low draw. Rates a genuine top-three candidate. MEADOWBROOK (3) has hit the frame in all three outings and looks ready for the step-up to the mile trip now. Keep in mind. IN SOCIETY (7) will be rock-hard fit now fourth-up from the break and may trouble the judge with any luck in running. LAAN (4) next in line for the Gollan/Jones combination.
